# Joo Feedback Compound

Use `rules/feedback-compound.md` when present.

- Emotion is not evidence.
- Compare exact expected requirement with diff/tests/tools/source.
- Correct the current task before reflection.
- Technical errors route to failure-triage.
- Root cause remains a hypothesis without independent evidence.
- Persist only repeated, expensive, high-severity, or explicit MUST NOT violations.
- New lessons apply from the next task and remain advisory.
- Skip stale lessons whose environment or anchors no longer match.
- Load at most three related lesson cards.
